channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Republican Moves To Defund IVF Ahead Of Presidential Debate
item.description: MAGA House Republican Matt Rosendale (R-MT) has filed an amendment to the defense spending bill to defund IVF.

item.title: The Great Paradox: How Unchecked Mass Migration Hurts Migrants

item.title: House Republican Embarrassingly Claims Biden Will Be Jacked Up On Mountain Dew At Debate
item.description: Rep. Eric Burlison (R-MO) floated that Biden has dementia, but then claimed that his campaign will jack him up with Mountain Dew at the debate.
